.TH DOTFILES 7 "2026-02-25" "dotfiles" "Dotfiles Reference"
.SH NAME
dotfiles \- personal system configuration reference
.SH DESCRIPTION
Quick reference for which config file controls what in this dotfiles setup.
All config files live in
.B ~/.dotfiles/
and are symlinked to their expected locations.
.
.SH CONFIGURATION FILES
All paths are relative to
.BR ~/.dotfiles/ .
.P
.TS
box tab(|);
cb | cb
l | l .
Setting|Config File
=
Window Manager|hyprland/hyprland.conf
Status Bar|waybar/config.jsonc + style.css
App Launcher|rofi/config.rasi
Notifications|dunst/dunstrc
Wallpaper|~/.config/hypr/hyprpaper.conf
Lock Screen|~/.config/hypr/hyprlock.conf
Terminal|ghostty/config
Editor|nvim/
Shell|zsh/zshrc
Login Shell (PATH)|zsh/zprofile
Local Overrides|~/.zshrc.local
Multiplexer|tmux/tmux.conf
Git|git/gitconfig
Man Page|man/dotfiles.7
.TE
.
.SH SYMLINKS
